history.content:
Tech + Social Impact is an organization that aims to create a tight-knit community in which members can explore, have candid conversations about, and take action on ways to use technology for social good. 

 

For Fall 2020, we are looking for students who have strong project management and technical skills to lead tech + social impact related projects across a variety of topics, including but not limited to education, health, and environmental science. All majors are welcome!

 

Apply to be a project lead at tinyurl.com/techimpactberkeley (due Tuesday 9/15, 11:59 pm PT)

 

If you have any questions, please contact us at techimpactberkeley@gmail.com. We look forward to reading your applications!
